OL,3,CMayor clashes with government over
OL,4,Cproposed Olympic bid for north of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FLondon's Labour mayor today clashed
OL,8,Fwith the government over a proposed
OL,9,FOlympic bid for the north of England.
OL,11,FA source close to the mayor said it
OL,12,Fwas a 'mistake' to ignore London.
OL,14,FMinisters have asked UK Sport to carry
OL,15,Fout a 'strategic assessment' ahead of
OL,16,Fa possible attempt to stage the
OL,17,FOlympic and Paralympic Games in the
OL,18,Fnorth in the 2040s.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
