FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779109901
OL,3,CMayor clashes with government over
OL,4,Cproposed Olympic bid for north of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FThe plan appeared to undermine Sir
OL,8,FSadiq Khan's proposals for a London
OL,9,FOlympics using sporting facilities
OL,10,Fbuilt for the 2012 games.
OL,12,FKhan first floated the idea of a
OL,13,Fproposed bid for the games during the
OL,14,FCovid-delayed 2021 mayoral election
OL,15,Fcampaign.
OL,17,FIn 2024 he suggested the 2040 games
OL,18,Fcould be the 'greenest Olympics ever"
OL,19,Fwith no need to build new sporting
OL,20,Fvenues.
OL,26,@zD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779109901
OL,3,CMayor clashes with government over
OL,4,Cproposed Olympic bid for north of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FBut any Olympic bid would rely on
OL,8,Fgovernment backing and today's
OL,9,Fannouncement suggested ministers are
OL,10,Flukewarm about London hosting its 4th
OL,11,Fgames.
OL,13,F"It's time the Olympics came North and
OL,14,Fwe showed what we can offer to the
OL,15,Fworld," said Culture Secretary Lisa
OL,16,FNandy MP.
OL,18,FShe added: "I couldn't be more pleased
OL,19,Fto announce that we're starting the
OL,20,Ffiring gun on a long overdue vote of
OL,21,Fconfidence in the North."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@GO]zD@LOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
