FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779109901
OL,3,CMayor clashes with government over
OL,4,Cproposed Olympic bid for north of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FCrucially, the Chancellor appears to
OL,8,Ffavour the north over London. Rachel
OL,9,FReeves MP said: "Britain's sporting
OL,10,Fprowess is recognised and respected
OL,11,Faround the world."
OL,13,FShe added: "It's something we are
OL,14,Fdetermined to capitalise on to breathe
OL,15,Flife into our communities and build a
OL,16,Fstronger and more secure economy.
OL,17,FThat's why we're throwing our full
OL,18,Fsupport behind bringing the Games back
OL,19,Fhome which will boost our Northern
OL,20,FGrowth Corridor."
OL,26,@qD@QOUsD@RO]uD@LOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
