PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779109901
OL,3,CMayor clashes with government over
OL,4,Cproposed Olympic bid for north of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Mayor of
OL,8,FLondon, said: "London is the sporting
OL,9,Fcapital of the world and the Mayor has
OL,10,Fopenly expressed his ambition for the
OL,11,Fcapital to be part of a future Olympic
OL,12,Fand Paralympic Games.
OL,14,FThe spokesperson continued: "Sadiq
OL,15,Fbelieves that a potential country-wide
OL,16,Fbid, using all the assets we have in
OL,17,Fthe UK, including the publicly-owned
OL,18,FLondon Stadium would deliver the very
OL,19,Fbest possible Olympics.
OL,26,@pD@OOUvD@]OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
