FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779109901
OL,3,CMayor clashes with government over
OL,4,Cproposed Olympic bid for north of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,F"Using London's existing world-class
OL,8,Finfrastructure would help deliver the
OL,9,Fgreenest and most sustainable Games,
OL,10,Fas well as unlocking huge economic
OL,11,Fgrowth both here in London and around
OL,12,Fthe country.
OL,14,F"Not including the capital in an
OL,15,FOlympics bid would be a missed
OL,16,Fopportunity, and mean our country
OL,17,Ffails to unleash the full benefits of
OL,18,Fa UK-wide games."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@QO]
