OL,3,CMayor clashes with government over
OL,4,Cproposed Olympic bid for north of
OL,5,CEngland
OL,7,FLondon's successful bid to host the
OL,8,F2012 games followed a failed attempt
OL,9,Fby Birmingham to stage the 1992 games
OL,10,Fand two unsuccessful bids by
OL,11,FManchester to host the 1996 and 2000
OL,12,FOlympics and Paralympics.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
